(7, 1, 'https://trustmark.gtri.gatech.edu/operational-pilot/trust-interoperability-profiles/ficam-loa-3-registration-and-issuance-profile/1.0/', 'FICAM LOA 3 Registration and Issuance Profile', '1.0', 'This Trust Interoperability Profile specifies FICAM LOA 3 requirements on subscriber registration and credential issuance by CSPs. This TIP is equivalent to the NIST 800-63 LOA 3 Registration and Issuance Profile, with the sole exception being that this TIP does not allow the use of derived credentials.', 'https://trustmark.gtri.gatech.edu/', 'GTRI NSTIC Trustmark Pilot', '2015-09-18 14:39:06.000865', '2016-11-01 10:44:22.000692', '2016-11-01 10:44:22.000692', '2016-11-01 10:44:22.000692', 1);  
